er spin-off series. In some instances, actors have portrayed potential ancestors, descendants, or relatives of characters they originated. Characters have also been recast for later appearances.\n\nBelow is an incomplete list:\n<!-- Use {{Efn-lg}} for in-line notes within this section -->\n<!-- Leave <div></div> to allow table to expand properly. -->\n<div style=\"overflow: auto;\">\n<!-- Limit to portrayals of characters (including familial relations) in more than one series, or recurring appearances by an actor who is also a main cast member of any other series. -->\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 90%; text-align: center;\"\n|-\n! style=\"min-width: 12em;\" |Actor(s)\n! style=\"min-width: 10em;\" |Character\n! style=\"min-width: 8em;\" |''[[Star Trek: The Original Series|The Original Series]]''{{Break}}{{Small|(1966\u20131969)}}\n! style=\"min-width: 8em;\" |''[[Star Trek: The Animated Series|The Animated Series]]''{{Break}}{{Small|(1973\u201374)}}\n! style=\"min-width: 8em;\" |''[[Star Trek: The Next Generation|The Next Generation]]''{{Break}}{{Small|(1987\u20131994)}}\n! style=\"min-width: 8em;\" |''[[Star Trek: Deep Space Nine|Deep Space Nine]]''{{Break}}{{Small|(1993\u20131999)}}\n! style=\"min-width: 8em;\" |''[[Star Trek: Voyager|Voyager]]''{{Break}}{{Small|(1995\u20132001)}}\n! style=\"min-width: 8em;\" |''[[Star Trek: Enterprise|Enterprise]]''{{Break}}{{Small|(2001\u20132005)}}\n! style=\"min-width: 8em;\" |''[[Star Trek: Discovery|Discovery]]''{{Break}}{{Small|(2017\u2013present)}}\n! style=\"min-width: 8em;\" |[[Star Trek: Short Treks|''Short Treks'']]{{Efn-lg|''[[Star Trek: Short Treks]]'' is a series of short films which do not form a cohesive story. There is no main cast.}}{{Break}}{{Small|(2018\u2013present)}}\n! style=\"min-width: 8em;\" |''[[Star Trek: Picard|Picard]]''{{Break}}{{Small|(2020\u2013present)}}\n|-\n|[[William Shatner]]\n|[[James T. Kirk]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cMain}}\n|{{cEmpty}}\n|{{CGuest|{{Small|Archive footage}}}}{{Efn-lg