ing}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Number One (Star Trek)|Number One{{\\}}Una]]\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{CGuest|{{Small|Archive footage}}}}{{Efn-lg|name=\"IfMemoryServes\"|Appeared in \"If Memory Serves\" via archive footage}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Rebecca Romijn]]\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|{{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Susan Oliver]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Vina (Star Trek)|Vina]]\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}{{Efn-lg|Susan Oliver was billed as a guest star in \"[[The Cage (Star Trek: The Original Series)|The Cage]]\", and appeared in \"[[The Menagerie (Star Trek: The Original Series)|The Menagerie]]\", Parts I and II, via archive footage.}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{CGuest|{{Small|Archive footage}}}}{{Efn-lg|name=\"IfMemoryServes\"|Appeared in \"If Memory Serves\" via archive footage}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Melissa George]]\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Roger C. Carmel]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Harry Mudd]]\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"7\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Rainn Wilson]]\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|{{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Phillip Pine]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |Philip Green\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"8\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|Steve Rankin\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Patrick Stewart]]\n|[[Jean-Luc Picard]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|{{cEmpty}}\n|{{CGuest|{{Small|Archive footage}}}}{{Efn-lg|name=\"TheseAretheVoyages\"}}\n|{{cEmpty}}\n|{{CGuest|{{Small|Archive footage}}}}{{Efn-lg|Appeared in \"Children of Mars\" via archive footage from \"Remembrance\" (''Picard'')}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Jonathan Frakes]]\n|[[William Riker]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n|{{cEmpty}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\