g, in episodes \"[[Borderland (Star Trek: Enterprise)|Borderland]]\", \"[[Cold Station 12]]\", and \"[[The Augments]]\"}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Wil Wheaton]]\n|[[Wesley Crusher]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}{{Efn-lg|Wil Wheaton's left the cast of the ''Next Generation'' in \"[[Final Mission]]\". He appeared in \"[[The Game (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|The Game]]\", \"[[The First Duty]]\", \"[[Parallels (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Parallels]]\" and \"[[Journey's End (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Journey's End]]\" as a guest.}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Diana Muldaur]]\n|[[Katherine Pulaski]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}{{Efn-lg|For each of her Season 2 appearances, Diana Muldaur was billed Special Guest.}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|Ann Mulhall\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"8\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[John de Lancie]]\n|[[Q (Star Trek)|Q]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Whoopi Goldberg]]\n|[[Guinan (Star Trek)|Guinan]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Jon Paul Steuer]]\n| rowspan=\"4\" |[[Alexander Rozhenko]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}{{Efn-lg|Jon Paul Steuer appeared in \"[[Reunion (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Reunion]]\".}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Brian Bonsall]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}{{Efn-lg|Brian Bonsall appeared in \"[[New Ground (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|New Ground]]\", \"[[Ethics (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Ethics]]\", \"[[Cost of Living (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Cost of Living]]\", \"[[Imaginary Friend (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Imaginary Friend]]\", \"[[Rascals (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Rascals]]\", \"[[A Fistful of Datas]]\", and \"[[Firstborn (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Firstborn]]\".}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[James Sloyan]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}{{Efn-lg|James Sloyan appeared as a future Alexander Rozhenko in \"[[Firstborn (Star Trek: The Next Generation)|Firstborn]]\".}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Marc Worden]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}{{Efn-lg|Marc Worden appeared in \"[[Sons and Daughters (Star Trek: Deep Space Nine)|Sons and Daughters]]\" and \"[[You Are Cordially Invited]]\".}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Jonathan Del Arco]]\n|[[Hugh (Star Trek)|Hugh]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n|Brian Brophy\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Bruce Maddox]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"6\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[John Ales]]\n| colspan=\"8\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n|[[Avery Brooks]]\n|[[Benjamin Sisko]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Ren\u00e9 Auberjonois]]\n|[[Odo (Star Trek)|Odo]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Terry Farrell (actress)|Terry Farrell]]\n|[[Jadzia Dax]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}{{Efn-lg|Terry Farrell left ''Deep Space Nine'' in \"[[Tears of the Prophets]]\".}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Nicole de Boer]]\n|[[Ezri Dax]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}{{Efn-lg|Nicole de Boer joined the cast of ''Deep Space Nine'' in \"[[Image in the Sand]]\".}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Cirroc Lofton]]\n|[[Jake Sisko]]\n| colspan=\"3\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Colm Meaney]]\n|[[Miles O'Brien (Star Trek)|Miles O'Brien]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cRecurring|Recurring}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Armin Shimerman]]\n|[[Quark (Star Trek)|Quark]]\n| colspan=\"2\" {{cEmpty}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n|{{cMain|Main}}\n|{{cGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{cEmpty}}\n|-\n|[[Alexander Siddig